{"tid":1221692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白杖=攻擊性武器？警方杯弓蛇影 失明人協進會︰非常荒謬","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T09:54:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3a615c167df2cd4d103fdbdc62f7ee9cd565f775","tid":1221692,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"警方連日來粗暴對待反對《逃犯條例》修訂的示威者，惹起公憤，更有警員疑「杯弓蛇影」，令視障人士險被誣蔑攜有攻擊性武器。香港失明人協進會昨發聲明指，有視障人士在6月9日在港鐵站附近遭到警方截停，並查問視障人士使用的白杖（盲人枴杖）是否攻擊性武器。會方怒轟警方行徑「非常荒謬」，並指修例已為社會帶來撕裂，要求港府暫緩審議修例草案。《蘋果》已向警方就事件查詢，正待回覆。<br />\n香港失明人協進會昨在Facebook專頁發聲明指，有視障會員稱在6月9日「反送中抗惡法」大遊行當日，在港鐵站附近被警員截停。期間警員一度質問視障人士使用的白杖是否攻擊性武器，直斥「這點實在非常荒謬。」<br />\n會方解釋，白杖是視障人士出行的必要工具，更是視障人士獨立自強的標誌，對警方竟截停視障人士並對白杖的用途有所懷疑深感失望，促請警方必須加強前線警務人員對殘疾人士的認識。<br />\n聲明亦表示，大批香港市民已就《逃犯條例》修訂草案，透過和平遊行、罷工罷課包圍立法會及政府總部的方式向政府表達憂慮，但只換來警方暴力鎮壓，令人心痛，促請特區政府先暫緩有關修例草案的審議，容許社會上有足夠的討論和細心聆聽市民各界對修例草案的意見，避免社會進一步撕裂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190614/large/1560497647_e883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190614%2Flarge%2F1560497647_e883.jpg&h=8c1318fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190614/59715007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59715007&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=af0c0d24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59715007&h=a32a8f5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190614/59715007</a>"},{"pid":"867091029cfeb54feec669d36bb1d8326768a94c","tid":1221692,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:22:42.000Z","msg":"仆街傷殘都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e95b9655fc2664660bc795e92f4e9ad78c74d6","tid":1221692,"uid":191291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:26:06.000Z","msg":"冇腦有個限度得唔得 你冇話你做咩出街 係咪想襲警"},{"pid":"b7c4377a37b7539058413a612828b06a53a0bf1d","tid":1221692,"uid":60764,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f1f53d976b43b43c3700ba17d7895fa610eacd3","tid":1221692,"uid":33848,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"屈個盲既偷睇國家機密"},{"pid":"8628771aff8ffcb86b91edf61985b0ea573b2a03","tid":1221692,"uid":59522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"毅進仔又助攻"},{"pid":"3493185a0056ad99dd3f1a4d4d6a3a9de3e48e00","tid":1221692,"uid":6548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:31:19.000Z","msg":"推出國際啦"},{"pid":"6abdce213fd38400f75ab0931821d903f0d739c5","tid":1221692,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f1f53d976b43b43c3700ba17d7895fa610eacd3","tid":1221692,"uid":33848,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"屈個盲既偷睇國家機密"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"正想入黎覆呢句"},{"pid":"87baa14afc23a4133f20e2aebc6a24d6ccd6fe9f","tid":1221692,"uid":252920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"呢班人真係好強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班黑警幾時變跛"},{"pid":"318c2e620684140b172024f3b49f5e2ea2d5a4e6","tid":1221692,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"盲既偷睇國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周星馳真係好有遠見"},{"pid":"16b51296bf2cad5da5941946a56d9207cd1e5221","tid":1221692,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"867091029cfeb54feec669d36bb1d8326768a94c","tid":1221692,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:22:42.000Z","msg":"仆街傷殘都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b8037decebf314ab0d2d4ffc23adb971eb8d36","tid":1221692,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bd4f5599d1784982b277c938f5b2def7ff93a7","tid":1221692,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:49:20.000Z","msg":"李星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> LOL上腦定中二病發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5479a9c93b58c367506e580c706861e7fb10688a","tid":1221692,"uid":71919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:49:31.000Z","msg":"助攻 香港大團結"},{"pid":"37e046c73e41c8412b505a336ad4bc91edcdcc16","tid":1221692,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（希望大家廣傳民陣fb呼籲！）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n毋忘年輕人付出，誓撤回逃犯條例！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣反送中遊行</span><br />\n日期：6月16日（星期日）<br />\n遊行開始時間：2:30pm<br />\n遊行起點：維多利亞公園<br />\n遊行終點：政府總部<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣三罷反送中集會</span><br />\n日期：6月17日（星期一）<br />\n集會地點：立法會外<br />\n當日行動：三罷（罷工罷市罷課）<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（留意返星期一嘅三罷集會係未有時間，要等民陣fb睇下佢地點安排）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗仲未完，一日未撤回惡法一日都仲有希望，政府宜家打算抄2014年拖字訣消耗民氣，希望大家可以廣傳民陣fb呼籲，最重要係出席遊行，重現一百萬人光景<br />\n<br />\n我地應該要接受香港和理非佔大多數呢個事實，大多數人都唔會衝始終法律後果太重，所以任何願意作出反惡法嘅和理非行動都應該要支持！（所以唔好再話有人企喺橋上面唔去打，上面99%都係和理非，肯出嚟已經好好，好過唔出嚟喺屋企睇電視嘅多多聲）香港人唔可以再比三毛分化，和理非同勇武必須一齊合作，佔大多數嘅和理非請用盡一切合法方法反對逃犯條例，逃犯條例絕對唔可以通過，否則我地同下一代就會生長喺講句說話都要就住就住，擔驚受怕嘅環境之中，大家絕對唔可以比逃犯條例過到<br />\n<br />\n我相信和理非係有佢嘅威力，可以喚起社會更多人關注，叧一方面亦同時爭取緊國際支持向政府施加壓力（eg取消美國香港關係法、各國商會嘅反對）去迫政府撤回逃犯條例。<br />\n<br />\n總之一句講曬：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n兄弟爬山</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df87d9c20e70f92daf0c13abfc82fa0a3660612","tid":1221692,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a615c167df2cd4d103fdbdc62f7ee9cd565f775","tid":1221692,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"警方連日來粗暴對待反對《逃犯條例》修訂的示威者，惹起公憤，更有警員疑「杯弓蛇影」，令視障人士險被誣蔑攜有攻擊性武器。香港失明人協進會昨發聲明指，有視障人士在6月9日在港鐵站附近遭到警方截停，並查問視障人士使用的白杖（盲人枴杖）是否攻擊性武器。會方怒轟警方行徑「非常荒謬」，並指修例已為社會帶來撕裂，要求港府暫緩審議修例草案。《蘋果》已向警方就事件查詢，正待回覆。<br />\n香港失明人協進會昨在Facebook專頁發聲明指，有視障會員稱在6月9日「反送中抗惡法」大遊行當日，在港鐵站附近被警員截停。期間警員一度質問視障人士使用的白杖是否攻擊性武器，直斥「這點實在非常荒謬。」<br />\n會方解釋，白杖是視障人士出行的必要工具，更是視障人士獨立自強的標誌，對警方竟截停視障人士並對白杖的用途有所懷疑深感失望，促請警方必須加強前線警務人員對殘疾人士的認識。<br />\n聲明亦表示，大批香港市民已就《逃犯條例》修訂草案，透過和平遊行、罷工罷課包圍立法會及政府總部的方式向政府表達憂慮，但只換來警方暴力鎮壓，令人心痛，促請特區政府先暫緩有關修例草案的審議，容許社會上有足夠的討論和細心聆聽市民各界對修例草案的意見，避免社會進一步撕裂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190614/large/1560497647_e883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190614%2Flarge%2F1560497647_e883.jpg&h=8c1318fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190614/59715007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59715007&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=af0c0d24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F59715007&h=a32a8f5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190614/59715007</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"向平機會投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b05b4b78ed21a77ea6d25baf9942d30763c394","tid":1221692,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}